paragraphs.title: Load ACM and DBLP datasets
paragraphs.text:
import spark.implicits._

val acmDF = spark.read.parquet("data/linkage-papers2/linkage-papers-acm.parquet")
println(s"Loaded ${acmDF.count} ACM records")
acmDF.cache()
acmDF.printSchema()

val dblp2DF = spark.read.parquet("data/linkage-papers2/linkage-papers-dblp2.parquet")
println(s"Loaded ${acmDF.count} DBLP records")
val groundTruthDF = spark.read.parquet("data/linkage-papers2/linkage-papers-acm-vs-dblp2.parquet")

val dblp2 = LuceneRDD(dblp2DF)
dblp2.cache()
dblp2.fields()

paragraphs.title: Compute Linkage Accuracy
paragraphs.text:
// Entity linkage
val linkedResults = dblp2.linkDataFrame(acmDF, linker, 3)


val linkageResults = spark.createDataFrame(linkedResults.filter(_._2.nonEmpty).map{ case (acm, topDocs) => (topDocs.head.doc.textField("id").get, acm.getInt(acm.fieldIndex("id")).toString)}).toDF("idDBLP", "idACM")

// Compute the number of currect results based on ground truth
val correctHits: Double = linkageResults.join(groundTruthDF, groundTruthDF.col("idDBLP").equalTo(linkageResults("idDBLP")) &&  groundTruthDF.col("idACM").equalTo(linkageResults("idACM"))).count

// Total # of ground truth records    
val total: Double = groundTruthDF.count

// Accuracy
val accuracy = correctHits / total

println("********************************")
println("********************************")
println(s"Accuracy of linkage is ${accuracy}")
println("********************************")
println("********************************")
